show.title: Raaja Re-Entry
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/FKUMWS
show.description: A businessman celebrates 25 years of his company, Patel Tech, which grew from nothing to a multimillion-dollar firm. He acknowledges the hard work of himself and his family. Now, he decides to return to India permanently to be with his wife and two sons after years of absence. He entrusts the company’s future and the launch of a new product to his team, assuring them they are capable of running it. While concerns are raised about his security as one of the world’s richest men, he stresses that his only wish is to spend the rest of his life with his family as an ordinary man.
